<br>
    Let me start by saying im fairly 'green' as far as overall EQ experience is concerned, have never been on a 'uberraid', nor really had a chance to see mobs that are gate capable...Even with all this in mind, i still have a hard time believing that VI is seriously making this line of &lt;cheese&gt; a reality  .....<br>
<br>
     In my mind, all this 'enhancement' does to benifit our class, is to grant us the same abilities GREEN mobs have had ALL along in the game....I mean, im gonna bust my arse to get through HELL LEVEL(s) so i can one day be capable(at the cost of x amount of mana) to do what mr. Kobold runt has been able to do since i started playing????  <br>
<br>
.....You begin to cast a spell.....(gate)<br>
.....a Kobold runt strikes YOU for 6 points of damage....<br>
.....your casting is interrupted.....<br>
<br>
<br>
ummmmmm, please, please, please someone tell me there's more to look forward to at higher levels that THIS.....getting ran out of a zone by a bloody green in OT because of resists is bad enough, but to think that one day I will be just as powerful as a lvl 1 mob leaves me with a sick feeling in my stomach......<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
